# Phase 10.2 — Docker Ignore
# Mega Fintrade Risk Monitor .NET
#
# This file keeps the Docker build context clean.
# It prevents local build outputs, IDE files, Git files, logs,
# local databases, and temporary files from being copied into the image.

# Git
.git
.gitignore

# GitHub workflow metadata is not required inside the runtime image
.github

# Visual Studio / VS Code / Rider
.vs
.vscode
.idea
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

# .NET build outputs
bin
obj
**/bin
**/obj

# Test results and coverage
TestResults
**/TestResults
coverage
**/coverage
*.coverage
*.coveragexml
coverage.cobertura.xml

# NuGet local artifacts
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
packages

# Logs
logs
Logs
*.log

# Local SQLite database files
*.db
*.db-shm
*.db-wal
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3

# Local environment files
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Docker files that do not need to be copied into the published app
docker-compose.yml
docker-compose.override.yml

# OS generated files
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# Temporary files
tmp
temp
*.tmp
*.temp
*.bak
*.swp

# Markdown/docs are not required for the runtime image
docs
*.md

# Node/frontend artifacts if accidentally added later
node_modules
npm-debug.log
yarn-debug.log
yarn-error.log
pnpm-debug.log